description: You'll love this tender chicken satay recipe. Just coat the tenderloins in mouth-watering satay, thread onto a skewer, bake in the oven and serve
keywords: Chicken dishes,Jun 2022,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,Low sugar,Chicken
name: Speedy Satay Chicken Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven grill on high. Line a large baking tray with foil. Soak bamboo skewers before using, or use metal skewers to save time.

Place chicken and sauce in a large bowl and mix to combine. Thread 1 chicken tenderloin onto each skewer. Place on tray and drizzle over oil. Grill for 20 minutes or until marinade has charred and chicken is cooked through.
Scatter coriander over chicken and serve with cucumber and onion.
